{{! Executive Application Rejected Email }}

<html>
  <head>
    <meta charset='utf-8' />
    <meta name='viewport' content='width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0' />
    <title>Application Update</title>
  </head>
  <body
    style="font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px;"
  >
    <div style='text-align: center; margin-bottom: 30px;'>
      <img src='{{logoUrl}}' alt='Skillancer' style='height: 40px;' />
    </div>

    <h1 style='color: #1a1a2e; font-size: 24px; margin-bottom: 20px;'>
      Update on Your Application
    </h1>

    <p>Hi {{firstName}},</p>

    <p>
      Thank you for your interest in joining the Skillancer Executive Suite. After careful review of
      your application, we're unable to move forward at this time.
    </p>

    {{#if reason}}
      <div style='background: #f8f9fa; border-radius: 8px; padding: 20px; margin: 24px 0;'>
        <p style='margin: 0; color: #666;'>
          <strong>Feedback:</strong>
          {{reason}}
        </p>
      </div>
    {{/if}}

    <p>
      This decision was based on our current criteria for
      {{executiveType}}
      executives, which includes specific experience requirements and market demand factors.
    </p>

    <h3 style='color: #1a1a2e;'>What's Next?</h3>

    <ul style='color: #666;'>
      <li style='margin-bottom: 12px;'>
        <strong>Reapply in 6 months:</strong>
        Our criteria evolves, and we encourage you to apply again.
      </li>
      <li style='margin-bottom: 12px;'>
        <strong>Join as a Freelancer:</strong>
        You may be a great fit for our general freelancer network.
        <br /><a href='{{freelancerUrl}}' style='color: #4f46e5;'>Learn more →</a>
      </li>
      <li style='margin-bottom: 12px;'>
        <strong>Stay Connected:</strong>
        Follow us for updates on new opportunities.
      </li>
    </ul>

    <p>
      We appreciate the time you invested in your application. We wish you the best in your
      executive career.
    </p>

    <p>
      Best regards,<br />
      <strong>The Skillancer Executive Team</strong>
    </p>

    <hr style='border: none; border-top: 1px solid #e5e7eb; margin: 30px 0;' />

    <p style='color: #999; font-size: 12px; text-align: center;'>
      ©
      {{year}}
      Skillancer. All rights reserved.<br />
      Questions? Contact
      <a href='mailto:executives@skillancer.com' style='color: #999;'>executives@skillancer.com</a>
    </p>
  </body>
</html>